pergunta: who argued with congress during the early years of reconstruction

pergunta: in humans what determines the gender of the offspring

During fertilization  if an X-bearing sperm fertilizes an egg  the resulting offspring will be a female (XX). If a Y-bearing sperm fertilizes an egg  the resulting offspring will be a male (XY).
